            <h1>📊 Inventory Forecasting</h1>
            <p class="subtitle">Intelligently predict future inventory needs using sales velocity, lead time, and historical data to prevent stockouts and optimize replenishment.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="alert alert-info">
            Total Inventory Units: <strong><%= totalQuantity %></strong> |
